title: #169 - The End Of An Era
description: On this extremely special episode of The H3 Podcast we take a look at all the best and worst moments of the podcast in the year 2019 (and one in 2018 because Ethan doesn't play by anyone's rules but his own). Come take a journey through the past with us and reexperience the many highs and lows of the greatest podcast in the world (the H3 Podcast).
